# Formspree Configuration
# Get your form ID from https://formspree.io/
# 1. Go to https://formspree.io/ and sign up
# 2. Create a new form in the dashboard
# 3. Copy ONLY the form ID (e.g., xykdwqay) - NOT the full URL
# Example: VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=xykdwqay
# You can also paste the full URL and it will extract the ID automatically
VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=your_formspree_id_here
